gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.admin

Class UtilizationSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.admin.UtilizationSummary

  • public final class UtilizationSummary
extends java.lang.Object

    Encapsulates summary statistics for a Utilization Report.

    Per Effective Java Item 17, this class is marked final because it was not designed for inheritance.

        public int getSecondsToFirstRunAverage()
        Returns the mean of HistoricalCalculation.getSecondsToFirstRun(). If there are no calculations, returns -1 like getSecondsToSignAverage() below.

      • getSecondsToSignAverage

        public int getSecondsToSignAverage()
        Returns the mean of SignedResult.getSecondsToSign(). If there are no signed calculations, returns -1. (Normally we would use an Optional for this, but it is not EL-friendly.)
